Objective
Automate daily data refresh from SQL Server to reporting layer.
________________________________________
ADF Pipeline Workflow
SQL Server Source
        ↓
ADF Copy Activity
        ↓
Data Validation
        ↓
Processed Reporting Layer
        ↓
Power BI Refresh
________________________________________
ADF Activities
Activity	Purpose
Copy Activity	Load daily hospital data
Stored Procedure	Validate occupancy metrics
Lookup Activity	Fetch latest records
Trigger	Daily scheduled refresh
Failure Alert	Notify admin on ETL failure
